09:55.064 --> 09:56.602
I can't hear you.

10:01.061 --> 10:02.983
- (INAUDIBLE)
- (FLAMES FLARE)

10:06.511 --> 10:07.829
Too late...

10:24.055 --> 10:26.211
(NATIVE MUSIC)

10:28.850 --> 10:31.210
Freya, you did this?

10:39.120 --> 10:43.656
You left me. Just abandoned me...

10:43.761 --> 10:45.176
