11:00.041 --> 11:01.632
MUM!!!

11:02.259 --> 11:04.037
Freya!

11:08.492 --> 11:09.647
Freya!

11:11.281 --> 11:15.605
You left me. No hope.

11:17.433 --> 11:19.819
Come. Come.

11:20.929 --> 11:23.038
(BOTH GRUNTING)

11:23.883 --> 11:24.971
AH!

11:38.290 --> 11:39.770
Something is burning.

11:40.623 --> 11:41.561
Yeah.

11:51.957 --> 11:55.517
(GRUNTS)

12:23.733 --> 12:25.780
(THRILLING MUSIC)

12:30.886 --> 12:31.917
Dan!

12:32.907 --> 12:33.948
Let's get him down!

12:34.000 --> 12:34.836
Dan.

12:35.819 --> 12:36.788
Dan!

12:37.181 --> 12:38.636
(SHE GRUNTS)

12:38.756 --> 12:41.956
(COUGHS AND GRUNTS)

12:46.865 --> 12:48.271
(DAN SCREAMS)

12:50.531 --> 12:53.356
Got him? Le... let's go!

12:56.675 --> 12:57.635
Come on.

13:07.285 --> 13:11.450
She... collapsed. I... I brought her here.

13:11.500 --> 13:13.605
- What's happened?
- I don't know.

13:13.640 --> 13:15.814
I'll... I'll get the doctor.

13:15.886 --> 13:20.958
Could I get some help?!
Ma'am? Can you hear me?

13:23.160 --> 13:24.396
