13:24.513 --> 13:25.353
All right.

13:29.966 --> 13:31.851
They've found Freya!

13:31.886 --> 13:33.681
- Where is she?
- In the hospital.

13:34.980 --> 13:36.002
I'll go!

13:42.319 --> 13:46.224
Natalie? What's the matter? Are you okay?

13:48.413 --> 13:49.890
Fuck, what have you done?

13:49.956 --> 13:54.761
Well it st... it started through
the night. It's... it's like...

13:55.299 --> 13:57.387
