14:02.684 --> 14:05.220
(CRYING) I just wanna claw my
own eyes out like that Russian...

14:05.265 --> 14:09.118
Okay. Okay, come on. I'm taking you to
the hospital. Come on. Come on, stand up.

14:09.517 --> 14:10.689
- (GRUNTS)
- Okay.

14:12.752 --> 14:13.936
(FREYA BREATHING HEAVILY)

14:13.989 --> 14:17.792
Freya? Freya? Freya, baby.

14:17.870 --> 14:23.210
What's happening to you? Freya...
Freya, where the hell have you been?

14:23.845 --> 14:26.972
I... found him.

14:27.007 --> 14:31.231
Found, found who, honey,
found who? Who is this guy?

14:32.801 --> 14:34.613
He saved me.

14:34.654 --> 14:37.003
W-what do you mean, saved you? Freya!

14:37.065 --> 14:39.707
- You have to calm down!
- I'm calm!

14:39.782 --> 14:40.737
Dad.

14:40.986 --> 14:41.916
What?

14:41.998 --> 14:46.843
With Freya's condition, this
kind of exertion is dangerous.

14:46.925 --> 14:51.589
Rest, peace and quiet.
Give her some time. Please.

14:51.624 --> 14:53.491
- (FREYA BREATHING HEAVILY)
- (MONITOR BEEPING)

15:03.942 --> 15:07.396
Dad. The man who brought her here?

15:08.367 --> 15:09.495
Vladek.

15:10.289 --> 15:12.266
We'll find him, stop him.

15:13.327 --> 15:18.484
Yeah, how's that? Same way
you find out who killed Hildur?

15:20.000 --> 15:24.541
There's just you and Petra.
Eric's gone AWOL and Dan...

15:25.470 --> 15:28.016
Dan's been tortured by a maniac.

15:33.560 --> 15:35.396
Petra can't find the car.

15:37.081 --> 15:40.483
- What car?
- Hildur's car. It's gone.

15:40.518 --> 15:43.925
Vanished. Disappeared. Her
car is not in Fortitude.

15:44.015 --> 15:48.180
Wherever she went,
that's where she left it.

15:53.161 --> 15:57.040
Come on, girl! I can't
just sit here doing nothing.

16:06.960 --> 16:09.565
Who did this to you?

16:09.634 --> 16:15.915
The shaman. The young
electrician. Vladek Klimov.

16:15.985 --> 16:20.419
Murdered Tomak and Hindemith,
fucking nailed me to a pit-prop.

16:21.480 --> 16:24.831
Also drums and dancing.

16:25.960 --> 16:27.503
We need to get you to the hospital.

16:27.569 --> 16:33.860
You need stitches and pain killers.
Jesus, Dan, you must be in agony.

16:33.895 --> 16:37.394
No. Pain's good, Petra.

16:39.175 --> 16:40.755
I need sleep now.

16:43.642 --> 16:45.934
Be out of my body for a while.

16:49.390 --> 16:50.926
Not over yet.

16:59.843 --> 17:01.756
What the hell is he talking about?

17:04.959 --> 17:07.013
I think we should get ready.

17:16.440 --> 17:18.224
The bear that Michael Lennox killed.

17:18.285 --> 17:21.073
The-the-the dead reindeer that me and
Natalie found, the Russian soldier...

17:21.108 --> 17:23.383
all of them. Similar
things with their eyes.

17:23.417 --> 17:26.001
- And what happened to me is...
- I don't know what to say.

17:26.042 --> 17:28.420
Please. She's in agony. I don't
have any expertise in this.

17:28.454 --> 17:30.511
Please, you have to
help me. I... I-I-I-I...

17:30.580 --> 17:32.501
She says she's never felt
pain like this before.

17:32.536 --> 17:37.592
- She'd be better here.
- Yes. Yes.

17:37.657 --> 17:40.182
These facilities, we could stabilise
her, and together, we can run

17:40.248 --> 17:42.853
all the necessary tests much
quicker than Adebimpe can.

17:42.905 --> 17:45.590
- I should bring her here.
- If you think that's best, Vincent.

17:46.224 --> 17:47.214
Okay.

17:50.900 --> 17:53.998
Would you please not keep
looking up at his office when I'm

17:54.033 --> 17:55.508
answering your questions about him.

17:55.543 --> 17:57.580
I'm sorry, Ralfi.

17:57.638 --> 17:58.794
(RALFI SIGHS)

18:02.680 --> 18:05.117
You told Hildur where to find Munk?

18:05.180 --> 18:09.415
That's right. He was at
the sink-hole in the road.

18:09.471 --> 18:11.671
Waiting for Kim Hopperstad.

18:12.831 --> 18:15.864
- Where is this sink-hole?
- The cement factory.

18:15.936 --> 18:20.720
Now, would you please sign Hildur's
condolences book as if that's

18:20.789 --> 18:22.675
what you came in here to do?

18:43.889 --> 18:45.483
I'll sign it later.

18:46.673 --> 18:49.102
They dragged him in an hour ago.

18:49.437 --> 18:52.133
He's unconscious in a police cell.

18:52.720 --> 18:57.683
Whoever took him drove
nails through his hands.

18:57.753 --> 19:01.491
And gave him some kind of drug, thank God.

19:03.088 --> 19:10.530
Doctor Khatri, you better pray that
he doesn't remember any of this!

19:26.033 --> 19:30.685
He met her here. Or she
drives out here and meets him.

19:30.763 --> 19:32.725
Wherever this sink hole is.

19:34.899 --> 19:36.315
And he kills her.

19:38.241 --> 19:39.561
Murders her.

19:42.987 --> 19:44.752
Where's the car?

19:45.486 --> 19:46.928
There's nothing here.

19:49.391 --> 19:51.992
I can see that there's nothing here!

19:58.159 --> 20:01.045
Hildur saw right through Munk.

20:01.134 --> 20:05.910
He had her fired, he made Eric the Sheriff.

20:05.945 --> 20:10.052
Dad, everything you say may well
be true, but right now, out here,

20:10.103 --> 20:13.573
with nothing to go on,
it's all just speculation.

20:13.624 --> 20:14.766
I have to pee.

20:30.837 --> 20:34.662
DAD?! IT'S HERE! IT'S HERE!

20:44.550 --> 20:46.306
Dad, look here.

20:50.248 --> 20:53.644
She met Munk. He killed her.

20:54.498 --> 20:56.966
He moved her body and he hid her car.

20:57.001 --> 21:00.296
Oh, wait. Her bag.

21:00.340 --> 21:01.363
What?

21:08.390 --> 21:11.093
- No. Her phone's not here.
- Under the seats.

21:16.880 --> 21:19.209
- There's nothing there.
- Damn it.

21:40.371 --> 21:41.667
- (GRUNTS)
- (WATER DRIPPING)

21:45.920 --> 21:50.385
Munk didn't move her. The currents did.

21:51.080 --> 21:55.296
These sinkholes, they open up
all... all the time around here.

21:55.364 --> 21:59.666
The water from the hot springs
runs right under here and on out

21:59.733 --> 22:00.990
into the bay...

22:01.893 --> 22:03.133
Where we found her.

22:06.102 --> 22:11.789
She confronted Munk, and
then he pushed her in.

22:13.800 --> 22:16.243
Or he threw her in after he killed her.

22:16.304 --> 22:20.118
- That son of a bitch.
- Dad. Please. You may be right.

22:20.153 --> 22:22.282
But we have no proof of any of this.

22:22.665 --> 22:24.346
(SCOFFS) Proof!

22:26.723 --> 22:28.338
You need proof.

22:28.373 --> 22:30.964
Yeah. That's right.

22:31.814 --> 22:32.910
Come on. Let's go.

22:34.079 --> 22:35.702
There's nothing we can do here.

22:35.748 --> 22:37.108
We should be with Mum.

23:12.713 --> 23:15.896
(GROANS)

23:53.555 --> 23:54.727
(SIGHS)

24:02.274 --> 24:03.674
(SIGH)

24:15.766 --> 24:19.365
(GRUNTS AND SNIFFS)

24:27.491 --> 24:29.124
