27:02.418 --> 27:04.547
This is the end stage, Michael.

27:05.755 --> 27:08.405
There's nothing I can do for Freya.

27:08.526 --> 27:11.653
Soon she'll be safe in
the arms of our Lord.

27:18.467 --> 27:20.162
(MONITOR BEEPING)

27:20.197 --> 27:22.491
- Oh, God. Oh, God...
- Stop her.

27:22.565 --> 27:26.478
- Hey, hey, hey, hey...
- Talk to her. Calm her down.

27:26.518 --> 27:27.665
Let me go...!

27:27.700 --> 27:31.107
It's okay! It's okay,
Natalie! I've got you.

27:31.197 --> 27:33.542
Let me go!

27:33.602 --> 27:37.041
It's okay. Dr. Khatri is
going to take some tests.

27:37.076 --> 27:38.574
- Okay?
- (BREATHING RAPIDLY)

28:00.785 --> 28:02.632
It's time.

28:02.692 --> 28:04.278
Get down on the floor now!

28:13.805 --> 28:17.325
So is it your first time?
Making love to an English man?

28:17.809 --> 28:19.840
(RUNE AND YEVA LAUGHING)

28:21.603 --> 28:23.878
Nobody is making any love to anybody.

28:23.913 --> 28:26.536
Love doesn't enter into
anything. So please shut up.

28:26.630 --> 28:28.010
Hey.

28:28.120 --> 28:31.085
I don't want to hear that kind
of talk, neither does your mother.

28:31.120 --> 28:34.175
You want to hear everything,
don't you, Mum? Gory details.

28:34.210 --> 28:36.789
(THEY LAUGH)

28:36.863 --> 28:38.868
All the ins and outs.

28:38.960 --> 28:39.872
Hey!

28:41.883 --> 28:43.321
(SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE)

28:49.171 --> 28:52.620
First time I saw Yeva,
it was in the forest.

28:52.675 --> 28:54.314
(RUNE CONTINUES SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

28:54.360 --> 28:56.868
I'm lost, Michael.

28:58.848 --> 29:05.013
You found me in the snow.
Held me in your arms.

29:05.124 --> 29:07.483
Lifted me up, my love.

29:09.600 --> 29:12.537
Everything else is nothing.

29:16.961 --> 29:19.066
I love you, Michael.

29:22.888 --> 29:25.335
Let me go now, please.

29:25.370 --> 29:27.408
There's nothing you can do.

29:48.360 --> 29:49.545
NO.

30:03.906 --> 30:04.758
Mum.

30:17.693 --> 30:19.639
(PETRA BREATHING DEEPLY)

30:19.800 --> 30:20.713
He's here now?

30:20.748 --> 30:23.269
Yes. Shall we discuss a strategy?

30:23.323 --> 30:24.817
Interview strategy?

30:25.683 --> 30:27.774
One thing I've been thinking...

30:27.849 --> 30:29.998
one thing I need you to help me with...

30:30.066 --> 30:31.431
let me check your gun.

30:32.373 --> 30:33.350
What?

30:40.776 --> 30:42.815
- Okay.
- No!

30:44.964 --> 30:46.345
(DOOR BUZZES, SLAMS SHUT)

30:47.880 --> 30:51.365
Let me out of here, Dan! DAN!

30:51.893 --> 30:53.081
Dan!

31:25.256 --> 31:26.506
(DIALING)

31:30.408 --> 31:31.240
Gah!

31:33.497 --> 31:37.950
Ingrid, it's me, come round here
as fast as you can, this is all

31:37.985 --> 31:39.578
going really bad!

31:43.550 --> 31:44.424
AH!

31:50.146 --> 31:52.488
Spilt blood and broken bones.

31:57.841 --> 32:03.141
I'm here... to bring you back.

32:06.858 --> 32:13.482
Dan Anderssen. Is he a
good sheriff or bad sheriff?

32:13.834 --> 32:19.279
You know what I've discovered?
I'm both, I'm all the sheriffs.

32:19.476 --> 32:21.750
I'm all the sheriffs
there's ever fucking been.

32:24.273 --> 32:27.910
I am always here when he comes.

32:28.721 --> 32:31.966
My father, my grandfather,
we are all the same.

32:32.001 --> 32:36.326
We were always there
and always will be there.

32:36.400 --> 32:37.634
And the people you killed?

32:37.681 --> 32:42.970
Those are only lives.
Blood and bones and bodies.

32:43.512 --> 32:46.638
I am saving their souls.

32:46.709 --> 32:48.148
And I'm your demon.

32:53.983 --> 32:56.338
(WET CRUNCHING)

32:56.373 --> 32:59.053
- (HE COUGHS)
- (DAN BREATHING DEEPLY)

33:09.098 --> 33:13.331
I took Elena's body
from your father's house.

33:18.000 --> 33:19.580
You can't know that!

33:23.124 --> 33:24.636
You don't know that!

33:25.903 --> 33:27.645
YOU'RE LYING!

33:28.569 --> 33:30.994
HOW COULD YOU KNOW THAT?!

33:41.080 --> 33:44.125
Ralfi? Ralfi? It's Petra.

33:44.183 --> 33:47.863
I'm in the police station, you
have to come and let me out.

33:49.586 --> 33:51.180
WHERE IS SHE NOW?!

33:53.640 --> 34:03.040
She's here. You were right before...
I... ran away. But... I'm back.

34:03.168 --> 34:06.191
El-Elena. She's here.

34:06.226 --> 34:07.790
Tell me where Elena is.

34:07.851 --> 34:10.658
She's here with us. She's always here.

34:10.716 --> 34:12.663
You can't escape her.

34:19.574 --> 34:21.500
Speak to her, Dan.

34:24.289 --> 34:25.514
You...

34:28.902 --> 34:30.027
you...

34:30.654 --> 34:32.679
speak to her.

34:35.109 --> 34:36.451
Dan!

34:38.498 --> 34:42.174
Speak... to me.

34:45.735 --> 34:47.023
(IN ELENA'S VOICE) Dan.

34:48.981 --> 34:49.958
Dan.

34:57.134 --> 34:59.267
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

34:59.960 --> 35:01.367
Here I am.

35:03.713 --> 35:05.425
Where we started.

35:06.329 --> 35:10.507
You and me. In this room.

35:12.920 --> 35:16.217
You asked me if I felt safe in Fortitude.

35:18.313 --> 35:23.835
And I thought it was...
a strange thing to ask.

35:26.801 --> 35:29.125
Is Fortitude safe?

35:29.185 --> 35:32.830
I don't know. How can I know?

35:32.943 --> 35:37.582
Maybe. Fortitude needs you.
There is a terrible thing to hand.

35:37.617 --> 35:40.947
And now you are strong
enough... to conquer it.

35:42.096 --> 35:43.286
What thing?

35:45.888 --> 35:49.693
It's not this boy who'll
kill the demon. It's you.

35:49.760 --> 35:51.759
It can only be you, Dan.

35:59.361 --> 36:04.171
If you can see me in your
heart, then you're Dan.

36:06.168 --> 36:11.015
If you keep me there,
you will always be Dan.

36:12.200 --> 36:14.827
And Fortitude will be safe.

36:17.760 --> 36:19.272
Only Dan.

36:28.696 --> 36:29.990
Too late.

36:32.077 --> 36:33.858
(THRILLING MUSIC)

36:38.421 --> 36:39.742
(BLOWS LAND IN DISTANCE)

36:52.087 --> 36:53.392
(KEYPAD BEEPS)

37:01.521 --> 37:05.561
Eight. Five. Two. One.

37:05.615 --> 37:07.439
Four. Zero. Four.

37:09.122 --> 37:10.348
He's killing him in there.

37:10.406 --> 37:14.251
Stay here, Ralfi! Stay away!
And call Doctor Adebimpe!

37:14.316 --> 37:15.246
Okay.

37:26.359 --> 37:31.126
DAN! STOP! PLEASE, DAN!

37:35.400 --> 37:36.836
DAN!

37:37.595 --> 37:38.644
PLEASE!

37:40.542 --> 37:41.502
(GUNSHOT)

37:44.742 --> 37:46.342
(GUNSHOT)

37:47.237 --> 37:48.230
No!

37:50.234 --> 37:52.482
Please, Dan. Please stop!

37:54.158 --> 37:55.758
(GUNSHOT)

37:58.015 --> 37:59.316
I'll shoot you.

38:01.375 --> 38:07.326
This is my choice. I
choose to save Fortitude.

38:08.680 --> 38:10.032
From you.

38:10.067 --> 38:12.192
(THRILLING MUSIC INTENSIFIES)

38:18.462 --> 38:19.814
(MUSIC STOPS)

38:21.664 --> 38:22.782
(MUNK SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY IN DISTANCE)

38:22.848 --> 38:24.241
I have no idea!

38:24.299 --> 38:27.823
I don't know if three people are
enough to do this sort of work.

38:27.885 --> 38:30.671
I... I've no experience
of this sort of work.

38:30.818 --> 38:31.398
(GUN COCKS)

38:31.433 --> 38:34.235
No, don't speak to
Khatri. I'll deal with her.

38:34.300 --> 38:38.502
She's-she's unpredictable, she's
irresponsible, i-it's her-her

38:38.558 --> 38:41.152
fucking fault we're in this mess.

38:41.257 --> 38:43.129
What the fuck are you...

38:45.209 --> 38:47.937
- End the call.
- I... I...

38:48.321 --> 38:49.298
(HE HANGS UP)

38:49.368 --> 38:50.403
(PHONE CLATTERS)

38:50.449 --> 38:52.730
(MUNK BREATHING RAPIDLY)

38:56.665 --> 38:58.750
- Get away from the window.
- What?

38:58.785 --> 39:00.414
This is a magnum and
the bullet will go right

39:00.461 --> 39:02.587
through your guts and
break the fucking window.

39:33.480 --> 39:36.808
- I haven't got any proof.
- What proof?

39:37.514 --> 39:40.011
You killed Hildur and I can't prove it.

39:40.069 --> 39:42.176
Oh. No, no. You-you know...

39:42.211 --> 39:44.998
- I should just shoot you right now!
- Please. No. No.

39:45.033 --> 39:49.593
- That would make everything better.
- You don't understand. No. No.

39:49.675 --> 39:53.155
Your wife's sick. Freya.

39:56.752 --> 39:57.860
Yes.

40:00.097 --> 40:01.719
What if I could help her?

40:06.458 --> 40:10.800
I work for a company. A
biomedical research company.

40:12.026 --> 40:15.405
- What they have found...
- What have they found?

40:15.440 --> 40:21.706
Exactly what she needs. Your
wife. Khatri's found a survivor.

40:21.845 --> 40:26.005
Someone with altered genetic qualities.

40:26.040 --> 40:30.380
Damaged tissues that can
recover to original health.

40:30.415 --> 40:32.420
A way to repair diseases.

40:32.560 --> 40:39.791
The Russians, they had one, all those
years ago, in that film we all saw.

40:39.877 --> 40:42.851
But... didn't know what it was.

40:44.200 --> 40:47.194
There is hope, Michael.

40:51.056 --> 40:56.543
Speak to Khatri. I'll speak
to Khatri too. We can both...

40:56.578 --> 40:57.937
(CLAMORING OUTSIDE)

41:08.362 --> 41:10.922
(GRUNTS)

41:37.263 --> 41:38.598
He's DEAD.

41:43.000 --> 41:47.885
He came to our town and did
terrible things amongst us.

41:48.005 --> 41:52.380
Brought blood and fear and madness.

41:54.400 --> 42:00.320
So now he joins them all in
death. And that was HIS OWN CHOICE.

42:25.958 --> 42:29.420
These are fully charged. Ten metre range.

42:30.921 --> 42:34.486
Might be too much clothing on
the target, so aim for the face.

42:41.900 --> 42:48.357
The darts are Fentanil. Impact
to dreamland about ten seconds.

42:51.790 --> 42:53.752
Anybody gets in the way...

42:59.360 --> 43:01.365
Who's the extraction?

43:01.413 --> 43:05.124
You're gonna like this.
It's their fucking Sheriff.

43:06.268 --> 43:08.165
Anything we should know?

43:08.200 --> 43:10.608
Bit of a character apparently.

43:51.760 --> 43:53.749
Teeny little lights.

43:56.000 --> 43:58.080
All gone, Hildur.

44:00.920 --> 44:03.104
All your little lights.

44:30.115 --> 44:31.715
(TEARING)

44:33.054 --> 44:34.359
(GASPS)

44:36.077 --> 44:38.530
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

44:44.570 --> 44:47.211
(MUSIC INTENSIFIES)

44:51.049 --> 44:53.410
Now all the light is mine.

44:58.359 --> 45:00.249
_

45:00.295 --> 45:02.877
It was a blessing you stopped him.

45:02.940 --> 45:05.027
A fucking blessing.

45:05.090 --> 45:06.560
I know what it is. I know what to do.

45:06.634 --> 45:08.557
There's nothing you can do for her. Ahh!

45:08.617 --> 45:11.645
Natalie, can you see... anything?
Can you see anything at all?

45:11.680 --> 45:12.967
There's nothing else now.

45:13.696 --> 45:15.024
(ALL YELLING)

